Name: Soep van Kana
Review Text: Great pricing, soup and service. Bread and butter are served free with the soup. Current pricing is 3,50€ M and 5,00€ L. Cozy and friendly atmosphere.

Name: Soep van Kana
Review Text: Excellent price and mission! 3.50€ for a big bowl of soup and 5€ for an enormous bowl of soup. They also have yummy sandwiches ( we had banana Brie and walnut)

Name: Soep van Kana
Review Text: Lovely place with nice and kind staff. Amazing tasty soups and organic tea. Very cheap and everything is great.

Name: Soep van Kana
Review Text: Awesome soups, friendly staff, great price and lovely coffee. A real little gem.
